      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEANINGFUL (1) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won two of three starts. Missed the frame latest (39.31) when sixth over 595m at this track in a Grade 6/MDN. Looks suited here and rates on top. MICKEY HALLER (2) crossed over from out wide but caught the leaders turning before drawing clear to score (31.01) at this track in a Grade 6 over 530m. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. OUR BEAVER (7) won again in another strong performance after leading them home to make it two in a row at Gawler over 643m (37.51). Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Can measure up again. WEBLEC STELLA (6) placed last time out so worth considering.",
